GDPR
## GDPR Clause

The Service Provider will process personal data only on documented instructions of the Customer. The provider shall implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure a level of security appropriate to the risk and shall assist the Customer in meeting its GDPR obligations, including data subject requests and breach notifications.

ISO
## ISO / Security Clause

The Service Provider maintains information security controls aligned with ISO/IEC 27001. Provider will provide evidence of controls upon request and comply with reasonable audit requests subject to confidentiality.

